node.text:
Summer shred challenge is now live on YT! Who's ready for summer?! (Not the aussies lol) Go give me some views, drop a like and comment, and I'll cook you a dinner.. 😁 
Comment if you're joining us for this challenge! #chloetingchallenge

#ad I had heaps of fun being a judge in @vspink PINK with Purpose project this year, thanks to all who submitted an entry. 15 amazing young adults received $25,000 each to pursue their dreams supporting mental health, sustainability, and to help their communities! Link in bio to learn more about the winners! Love this new outfit of theirs, catch in the the next program coming up IN A WEEK!

#chloetingchallenge
